         <li>This procedure establishes minimum requirements for the use and inspection of ladders to reduce the chance of an incident.</li>
         <li>This procedure does not cover requirements for scaffolding, lift safety or fall protection. Please refer to additional programs such as Working at Heights or Mobile Equipment regarding those topics.</li>
